    "long_instructions": "## Using JavaScript\r\n\r\nThis level has a basic webpage with a toggle and some starter JavaScript.\r\n\r\nThe toggle should change the page to your favorite color when turned on and then back to white when turned off.\r\n\r\nCan you use AI Tutor to get the toggle working?",
